
Usage: leshif-wol [-OPTION] [-OPTION] ...
       leshif-wol - m [hardware_address] -i [ip_address] -p [port]

Otions:
    -v  displays leshif-wol version
    -m  hardware_address -> required option
    -i  destination IP address -> default address: broadcast address
    -p  destination port -> default port: 9


